{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "8e5048f8-411b-41a6-96ba-4a5f07ac7c8c", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8e5048f8-411b-41a6-96ba-4a5f07ac7c8c@1.pkg/1772602212397/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602212663", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8e5048f8-411b-41a6-96ba-4a5f07ac7c8c@1.pkg/1772602212397/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602212663"}, "identifier": "8e5048f8-411b-41a6-96ba-4a5f07ac7c8c", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"margin-left: 0.15in;margin-right: -0.08in;text-align: justify;\"><span>B</span><span>卖炭翁受压榨受欺凌但不敢反抗的人物形象</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>C</span><span>&ldquo;卖炭翁，伐薪烧炭南山中&rdquo;运用叙述，&ldquo;满面尘灰烟火色，两鬓苍苍十指黑&rdquo;则是描写</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>D&ldquo;牛困人饥日已高&rdquo;七个字就间接写出了卖炭翁在雪地赶车行走的整个过程</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列分析正确的一项是（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "下列分析正确的一项是（    ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8e5048f8-411b-41a6-96ba-4a5f07ac7c8c@1.pkg/item.json?v=1745244334654", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;\">这是一首叙事诗，揭露了&ldquo;宫市&rdquo;的掠夺本质，反映了中唐以后统治阶层直接剥削、压迫人民的社会现实，表达了诗人对劳动人民的深切同情。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>全诗完整地记述了卖炭老人烧炭、运炭和卖炭的经过，刻画了卖炭翁受压榨受欺凌但敢于反抗的人物形象。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;卖炭翁，伐薪烧炭南山中&rdquo;运用叙述，&ldquo;满面尘灰烟火色，两鬓苍苍十指黑&rdquo;则运用说明表达方式，全诗笔法简洁，富有表现力。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;牛困人饥日已高&rdquo;七个字就直接写出了卖炭翁在雪地赶车行走的整个过程，形象地写出了卖炭翁卖炭的艰难困苦：路远、车重、雪厚、人苦。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列分析正确的一项是（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "$RE0200", "5036342748", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-